'''Didier Kamanzi''', umukinnyi wa filimi mu [[Rwanda]] <ref>https://mni.rw/CompetitionVote/485</ref>.  Umwe mu bakinnyi bazwi cyane muri sinema yo mu [[Rwanda]], Kamanzi azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri filime ''Rwasa'', ''Rwassibo'' na ''Catherine'' . 

Usibye gukina, ni n'umukinnyi mu ikipe y'igihugu ya rugby ubumwe bw'u [[Rwanda]] .<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/29428</ref><ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/70539/umukinnyi-wa-filime-didier-kamanzi-70539.html</ref> 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1994 mu [[Uburundi|Burundi]] nk'umwana wa gatatu w'umuryango ufite barumuna be batandatu. Nyuma ya jenoside yo mu [[Rwanda]], yasubiye mu [[Rwanda]] mu 1994 yiga mu mashuri yisumbuye. Yakoze nka bouncer muri club ya nijoro yaho amezi make<ref>https://frankensaurus.com/Didier_Kamanzi</ref>.<ref>https://www.africanews.com/2019/03/21/lions-de-fer-rugby-football-club-rfc-out-to-claim-rugby-league-title/</ref><ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/75905/kamanzi-didier-uri-mubahatanira-igihembo-cy-umukinnyi-wa-fil-75905.html</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Mugihe akora nka bouncer muri club nijoro, yabonye igitekerezo cyo kugerageza film. Yagiye muri auditions abona uruhare. Muri 2015, yatsindiye igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza mu bihembo bya firime yu [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/63209/ubwumvikane-buke-butumye-didier-kamanzi--63209.html</ref>.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/207029</ref><ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201506010357.html</ref> 

